{"tid":2303943,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【凍齡嫲嫲】與小鮮肉兒子被誤認情侶　53歲凍齡美魔女嫲嫲皮膚緊緻0贅肉","createTime":"2020-11-28T10:49:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T23:13:52.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4e24603aa6820e69953cb865966e3cd75f2a95ac","tid":2303943,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T10:49:55.000Z","msg":"女人唔keep好易老！印尼一名52歲Puspa Dewi就因為逆天的凍齡外貌，引起網民關注！雖然已經53歲，但她臉上幾乎看不到歲月的痕跡，與兒子合照時更被誤以為是情侶。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報道，這名53歲凍齡美魔女嫲嫲叫Puspa Dewi，已育有2名兒子，及1名孫兒。由於母子感情不錯，會經常一起外出，但因為她凍齡的外表，經常會被誤以為是兒子的女朋友。<br />\n<br />\nPuspa Dewi亦會經常在社交網站分享生活日常，最近她的大兒子與妻子生下兒子，晉升嫲嫲的她反而更似孫兒的媽媽。<br />\n<br />\n此外，她又會分享自己做運動的片段，表示經常鍛鍊、健康飲食及快樂的心態，是她的凍齡秘方。而且，從她貼出的22年前後對比照可見，她的身材仍然窈窕，無贅肉。<br />\n<br />\n她又分享與老公的多年前後對比照，可見老公已漸漸長出白髮、法令紋加深，但歲月沒在她身上留下痕跡，臉部仍然緊緻，皺紋較少，可謂愈活愈年輕。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2815000/2815157/grandma_thumb_20201128_S_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2815000%2F2815157%2Fgrandma_thumb_20201128_S_1024.jpg&h=e82ec1e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2815000/2815157/2906778-PH_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2815000%2F2815157%2F2906778-PH_1024.jpg&h=d41f010d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2815000/2815157/puspadewih_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2815000%2F2815157%2Fpuspadewih_1024.jpg&h=a4ca7579&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2815000/2815157/puspadewihc_120488359_535311570636864_4390450063211934494_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2815000%2F2815157%2Fpuspadewihc_120488359_535311570636864_4390450063211934494_n_1024.jpg&h=a8841738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2815000/2815157/puspadewihc_118601306_1197079757314024_8841310370674060227_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2815000%2F2815157%2Fpuspadewihc_118601306_1197079757314024_8841310370674060227_n_1024.jpg&h=5f695c7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2815000/2815157/puspadewihc_121603054_1261126777569118_8585642964107345180_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2815000%2F2815157%2Fpuspadewihc_121603054_1261126777569118_8585642964107345180_n_1024.jpg&h=b30b90e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2815000/2815157/puspadewihc_122155488_2762587803987802_9150122828689965510_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2815000%2F2815157%2Fpuspadewihc_122155488_2762587803987802_9150122828689965510_n_1024.jpg&h=90ea7ebc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51ee4e32230eb660ea476b7d672787e1bdc52e3a","tid":2303943,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T10:50:36.000Z","msg":"想啪啪啪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8348c9ddeb2d14c1f97a8c20e79d3c767666174","tid":2303943,"uid":46885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T10:51:08.000Z","msg":"望落仲後生咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bbe67fe6a78d647dc2f6fa24bd4b3f90a0c6e03","tid":2303943,"uid":48064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sco